StringValues.16: A smooth silver stone, warm to the touch. There is a symbol inscribed on one side; an eight-pointed starburst shape overlaid on a swirling portal. In the heart of the starburst is a crashing wave. Within the folds of the portal swirl are four glass beads, red, blue, violet, and green.
StringValues.14: This stone will imbue the proper object with unique magical properties.
